c: 2
v: 260
t: "And ЋєrememberЋЇ when Abraham said, вАЬMy Lord! Show me how you give life to the dead.вАЭ God responded, вАЬDo you not believe?вАЭ Abraham replied, вАЬYes I do, but just so my heart can be reassured.вАЭ God said, вАЬThen bring four birds, train them to come to you, Ћєthen cut them into pieces,ЋЇ and scatter them on different hilltops. Then call them back, they will fly to you in haste. And Ћєso you willЋЇ know that God is Almighty, All-Wise.вАЭ"